e="maintext" org="uniform" sample="complete" part="N"> <p>To Doc &amp; Mrs Bevan</p> </div> <div type="salute" org="uniform" sample="complete" part="N"> <p rend="indent">from</p> <p rend="indent">Ludwig Wittgenstein B.M.</p> </div> </div></body></text></TEI>